                <mxCell id="73" value="底层物理网卡（Tokio 异步设备）和上层虚拟路由器（smoltcp 同步状态机）之间不能直接对话，必须实现 &lt;div style=&quot;display:inline&quot; class=&quot;notion-inline-code-container&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;notion-enable-hover&quot; spellcheck=&quot;false&quot; data-token-index=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;SFMono-Regular&amp;quot;, Menlo, Consolas, &amp;quot;PT Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, Courier, monospace;line-height:normal;background:rgba(135,131,120,.15);color:#EB5757;border-radius:4px;font-size:85%;padding:0.2em 0.4em;position:relative;bottom:0.065em&quot;&gt;smoltcp::phy::Device&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt; 特征来作为“翻译官”（适配器）。" style="ellipse;shape=cloud;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
